IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: JCC OF MID WESTCHESTER IS A NONPROFIT COMMUNITY CENTER DEDICATED TO ENRICHING THE JEWISH COMMUNITY BY PROVIDING SERVICES, PROGRAMS, AND FACILITIES TO PEOPLE OF ALL AGES, RACES, OR RELIGIONS.
IRS990.MissionDesc: JCC OF MID WESTCHESTER IS A NONPROFIT COMMUNITY CENTER DEDICATED TO ENRICHING THE JEWISH COMMUNITY BY PROVIDING SERVICES, PROGRAMS, AND FACILITIES FOR PEOPLE OF ALL AGES. THE JCC SERVES TO ENHANCE THE EDUCATION, MENTAL AND PHYSICAL HEALTH, FAMILY LIFE, CULTURAL ENVIRONMENT, AND GENERAL WELFARE OF ITS MEMBERS; TO PRESERVE THE HERITAGE, VALUES, TRADITIONS, CULTURES, ETHICS AND PHILOSOPHY OF JUDAISM, AND TO PROMOTE INTERFAITH UNDERSTANDING AND COOPERATION BY WORKING TO FURTHER THE BEST INTERESTS OF THE ENTIRE COMMUNITY. THE SERVICES, PROGRAMS, AND FACILITIES, ARE AVAILABLE TO ALL, REGARDLESS OF RACE, COLOR, RELIGION, OR SEX. PARTICIPATION IN THE JCC IS OPEN TO ALL, REGARDLESS OF FINANCIAL CIRCUMSTANCES, AND SCHOLARSHIP AID IS AVAILABLE THROUGH INDIVIDUAL DEPARTMENTS.
IRS990.Desc: SPORTS AND FITNESS INCLUDE A FULL AQUATICS PROGRAM, CHILDREN'S GYMNASTICS, FITNESS CENTER AND PERSONAL TRAINING. DUE TO COVID WE CLOSED DOWN SOME OF OUR CLASSES AND WENT VIRTUAL WITH OTHERS. POPULAR CLASSES ARE ZUMBA, HIP HOP, YOGA AND TAI-CHI. CHILDREN'S PROGRAMS FEATURE, GYMNASTICS, SPORTS, KARATE AND SWIM. PROGRAMS SUPPORT THE HEALTH OF OVER 2000 PATRONS AND COMMUNITY MEMBERS. WE ARE AVAILABLE TO ALL REGARDLESS OF RACE, GENDER IDENTIFICATION, OR RELIGION.

ProgSrvcAccomActy2Grp.Desc: SUMMER CAMPS FOR 115 CHILDREN AGES 2-17. SUMMER DAYS AT THE J IS A TRADITIONAL DAY CAMP WITH SPORTS, ARTS, MUSIC, NATURE, SWIMMING AND SPECIAL EVENTS. CAMPERS WITH SPECIAL NEEDS ARE INTEGRATED WITH TRAINED STAFF AND DANCE INTENSIVE IS FOR ADVANCED DANCE STUDENTS. OUR GYMNASTICS SUMMER PROGRAMS ARE AVAILABLE TO BOYS AND GIRLS 3-17. OPEN TO ALL REGARDLESS OF RACE, GENDER IDENTIFICATION OR RELIGION.

ProgSrvcAccomActy3Grp.Desc: IN THE ARTS, OUR DANCE SCHOOL PROGRAMS HAVE OVER 125 PEOPLE AGED 3 YEARS TO SENIORS. WE OFFER BEGINNERS TO ADVANCED DANCE CLASSES ALL YEAR ROUND AND WE OFFER A COMMUNITY THEATRE FOR 4 WEEK FOR AGES 5-17 AT THE BENDHEIM THEATRE WHICH INCLUDES PERFORMANCES.

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION IS SUBJECT TO THE PROVISIONS OF THE FINANCIAL ACCOUNTING STANDARDS BOARD'S(THE "FASB") ACCOUNTING STANDARDS CODIFICATION ("ASC")TOPIC 740, INCOME TAXES, AS IT RELATES TO ACCOUNTING AND REPORTING FOR UNCERTAINTY IN INCOME TAXES. BECAUSE OF THE ORGANIZATION'S GENERAL TAX-EXEMPT STATUS,MANAGEMENT BELIEVES ASC TOPIC 740 HAS NOT HAD, AND IS NOT ANTICIPATED TO HAVE, A MATERIAL IMPACT ON THE ORGANIZATION'S FINANCIAL STATEMENTS.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 11B
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE DRAFT FORM 990 IS CIRCULATED TO THE AUDIT COMMITTEE OF THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS AND REVIEWED BY SUCH COMMITTEE, BEFORE IT IS FINALIZED AND FILED.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 12C
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION PROVIDES A WRITTEN COPY OF ITS CONFLICT OF INTEREST POLICY TO EACH BOARD MEMBER AT THE BEGINNING OF EACH YEAR. EACH BOARD MEMBER IS ASKED TO SIGN A COPY CONFIRMING THAT THEY ARE AWARE AND AGREE WITH THE POLICY. THE BOARD MEMBER IS RESPONSIBLE TO NOTIFY THE BOARD WHEN THEY BELIEVE A POTENTIAL CONFLICT EXISTS. ANY BOARD MEMBER THAT SUSPECTS A CONFLICT MAY EXIST WITH ANOTHER MEMBER IS FREE TO NOTIFY THE BOARD LEADERSHIP AS WELL.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 15
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION AND ITS BOARD USE COMPARABLE COMPENSATION DATA AND ANNUAL REVIEWS OF ITS EMPLOYEES IN ORDER TO DETERMINE THE APPROPRIATE LEVEL OF COMPENSATION FOR ITS EMPLOYEES.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION C, LINE 18
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE 990 IS AVAILABLE ON WWW.GUIDESTAR.ORG AND ON THE NYS CHARITIES BUREAU WEBSITE.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION C, LINE 19
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE GOVERNING DOCUMENTS AND FORM 990 ARE AVAILABLE UPON REQUEST.
